<main id="content" class="content article article--sidebar" tabindex="-1">
<div class="topper topper--side-by-side topper--caption">
<div class="topper-hgroup">
<p class="topper-overline">
<span class="topper-overline-inner">
<a class="topper-overline-link" href="https://www.thetrace.org/projects/long-shadow-in-guns-we-trust-podcast/">In Guns We Trust</a>
</span>
</p>
<h1 class="topper-hed topper-hed--big">The Armed Era</h1>
<p class="topper-dek">
Since the mass shooting at Columbine High School 25 years ago, guns have grown ubiquitous, showing up in grocery stores, airports and political protests, and encroaching on our lives in new and unprecedented ways.
</p>
<div class="article__meta">
<div class="article__byline">
<div class="article__byline__author">
By <a href="/author/jennifer-mascia/">Jennifer Mascia</a> and <a href="/author/chip-brownlee/">Chip Brownlee</a> </div>
<div class="article__byline__date">Apr 9, 2024</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="topper-asset">
<figure class="topper-asset-mod">
<div class="article-asset-mod">
<div class="lazy-img__mod article-asset ">
<span class="lazy-img__placeholder" style="padding-top: 66.68%"></span>
<img class="lazy-img lazyload " data-srcset="https://www.thetrace.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Albuquerque.jpeg 2500w, https://www.thetrace.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Albuquerque-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://www.thetrace.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Albuquerque-1024x683.jpeg 1024w, https://www.thetrace.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Albuquerque-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://www.thetrace.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Albuquerque-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w, https://www.thetrace.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Albuquerque-2048x1366.jpeg 2048w, https://www.thetrace.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Albuquerque-680x453.jpeg 680w" data-src="https://www.thetrace.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Albuquerque.jpeg" data-sizes="auto" alt data-caption data-credit />
</div>
</div>
</figure>
</div>
</div>
<div class="topper--side-by-side__caption">
<figcaption class="article-caption">
<div class="article-caption-width">
<span class="article-caption__description">Demonstrators carry assault weapons during a Second Amendment rally in Albuquerque, New Mexico, in 2023.</span>
<cite>Roberto E. Rosales/AP File</cite>
</div>
</figcaption>
</div>
<article class="article-body js-article-body js-article-body-content">
